{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "hdim-care-gaps-collection",
		"name": "HDIM - 04 Care Gaps",
		"description": "Care gap detection and closure workflows\n\n**Features:**\n- Identify open care gaps for patients\n- View gap details and recommendations\n- Close care gaps with evidence\n- Track gap closure progress",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "List Patient Care Gaps",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    if (jsonData.careGaps && jsonData.careGaps.length > 0) {",
							"        pm.environment.set(\"care_gap_id\", jsonData.careGaps[0].id);",
							"        console.log(\"✅ Found\", jsonData.totalCount, \"care gap(s)\");",
							"    }",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "X-Tenant-ID",
						"value": "{{tenant_id}}",
						"type": "text"
					}
				],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{care_gap_url}}/api/v1/patients/{{patient_id}}/care-gaps?status=OPEN&priority=HIGH",
					"host": [
						"{{care_gap_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"v1",
						"patients",
						"{{patient_id}}",
						"care-gaps"
					],
					"query": [
						{
							"key": "status",
							"value": "OPEN"
						},
						{
							"key": "priority",
							"value": "HIGH"
						}
					]
				},
				"description": "**Get open care gaps for a patient**\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"careGaps\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"GAP-54321\",\n      \"patientId\": \"PAT-12345\",\n      \"measureId\": \"DIA-HBA1C\",\n      \"gapType\": \"MISSING_LAB\",\n      \"status\": \"OPEN\",\n      \"priority\": \"HIGH\",\n      \"dueDate\": \"2026-02-15\",\n      \"recommendation\": \"Schedule HbA1c lab test\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Get Care Gap Details",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "X-Tenant-ID",
						"value": "{{tenant_id}}",
						"type": "text"
					}
				],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{care_gap_url}}/api/v1/care-gaps/{{care_gap_id}}",
					"host": [
						"{{care_gap_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"v1",
						"care-gaps",
						"{{care_gap_id}}"
					]
				}
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Close Care Gap",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "X-Tenant-ID",
						"value": "{{tenant_id}}",
						"type": "text"
					},
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json",
						"type": "text"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"closureReason\": \"LAB_COMPLETED\",\n  \"closureDate\": \"2026-01-25T00:00:00Z\",\n  \"notes\": \"HbA1c completed on 2026-01-25, value: 6.2%\",\n  \"evidenceResourceId\": \"LAB-12345\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{care_gap_url}}/api/v1/care-gaps/{{care_gap_id}}/close",
					"host": [
						"{{care_gap_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"v1",
						"care-gaps",
						"{{care_gap_id}}",
						"close"
					]
				},
				"description": "**Close a care gap with evidence**\n\n**Closure Reasons:**\n- `LAB_COMPLETED` - Required lab test completed\n- `PROCEDURE_COMPLETED` - Required procedure completed\n- `MEDICATION_PRESCRIBED` - Medication prescribed\n- `PATIENT_REFUSED` - Patient refused recommended care\n- `NOT_APPLICABLE` - Gap no longer applicable"
			},
			"response": []
		}
	]
}
